public class PostgreSQLMappedTableHandler extends MappedTableHandler
Mapped table handler for PostgreSQL that expects JSON-type columns for ColumnMapping.TYPE_JSON_LIST and ColumnMapping.TYPE_JSON_MAP property mappings.
